.SP 5 5
We have a bed for all professions, even assassins have been known to
comment on the soft and sily smoothness of a Bedded Beauties bed.  We have
beds in the height of style.

<picture>A woman is lying on the sheets, looking slightly glazed and
satisfied at a man lying in the bed beside her.  You can just see the flash
of a knife in her hand, poised.  The bed is a black double bed with
black sheets and at the bottom is a note saying 'Waterproof sheets
extra'.</picture>
